name: Lophomyrtus obcordata (Raoul) Burret
habitat: Margin of pocket of forest. Podocarpus totara, Dacrycarpus dacrydioides, Alectryon excelsus / divaricating small trees.
locality: near Tikokino, Gwavas, paddock between eastern end of Puahanui Bush and homestead.
